---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Event Calendar" description="Annual calendar of Master Mariners Benevolent Association events — regatta, wooden boat show, Jessica Cup, cruises, potlucks, and social gatherings on San Francisco Bay.">

  <div class="hero-band">
    <h1>MMBA Event Calendar</h1>
    <p>Annual schedule of events on San Francisco Bay</p>
  </div>

  <main>
    <h1>Annual Calendar of Events</h1>

    <p>
      The Master Mariners Benevolent Association maintained a rich annual calendar of sailing events, social gatherings, and cruises throughout the year on San Francisco Bay.
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Archive Notice</h3>
      <p>This calendar reflects the historical event schedule of the MMBA. For current sailing events on San Francisco Bay, please refer to the individual yacht clubs and organizations listed in our <a href="/links">maritime links directory</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Annual Events Schedule</h2>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Month</th><th>Event</th><th>Location</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>January</td>
          <td><strong>New Year's Day Cruise</strong> — Traditional start-of-year sail</td>
          <td>San Francisco Bay</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>March</td>
          <td><strong>Membership Renewals Due</strong> — Annual dues renewal deadline</td>
          <td>—</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>May (Memorial Weekend)</td>
          <td><strong>Annual Master Mariners Regatta</strong> — The flagship event; 75–100 vessels</td>
          <td>St. Francis YC start · Encinal YC finish</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>May (Friday before Regatta)</td>
          <td><strong>Sponsors Luncheon</strong> — House flag drawing ceremony</td>
          <td>St. Francis YC</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>May/June</td>
          <td><strong>Spring Potluck</strong> — Member gathering and social</td>
          <td>TBD annually</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Late June / Early July</td>
          <td><strong>Annual Wooden Boat Show</strong> — Open to the public</td>
          <td>Corinthian YC, Tiburon</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Late July / August</td>
          <td><strong>Spaulding BBQ</strong> — Summer gathering at Spaulding Wooden Boat Center</td>
          <td>Sausalito</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>September</td>
          <td><strong>Labor Day Cruise</strong> — Extended sailing cruise</td>
          <td>San Francisco Bay / Delta</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>September</td>
          <td><strong>River Rat Cruise</strong> — Sacramento Delta cruise</td>
          <td>Sacramento River Delta</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>October</td>
          <td><strong>Jessica Cup Regatta</strong> — Gaff-rig and traditional yacht race</td>
          <td>St. Francis YC</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>October / November</td>
          <td><strong>Drake's Bay Cruise</strong> — Offshore cruise to Drake's Bay</td>
          <td>Drake's Bay, Marin</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>December</td>
          <td><strong>Annual Meeting &amp; Holiday Gathering</strong></td>
          <td>TBD annually</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Key Annual Events</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/regatta">Annual Regatta</a> — The centerpiece of the MMBA year</li>
      <li><a href="/boatshow">Wooden Boat Show</a> — Summer celebration of traditional craft</li>
      <li><a href="/jessica">Jessica Cup</a> — Autumn gaff-rig race</li>
      <li><a href="/drakes">Drake's Bay Cruise</a> — Offshore adventure</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-top:2rem"><a href="/regatta">&larr; Regatta Details</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/links">Maritime Links &rarr;</a></p>
  </main>
</Layout>
